@WeatherApi_HostAddress = http://localhost:5021

### Create a shortened URL
POST {{WeatherApi_HostAddress}}/api/urls
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "url": "https://example.com/articles/building-a-url-shortener",
  "expirationInMinutes": 60,
  "outputType": "shortUrl"
}

### Create a QR code that points to the shortened URL
POST {{WeatherApi_HostAddress}}/api/urls
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "url": "https://example.com/articles/building-a-url-shortener",
  "outputType": "qrCode"
}

### Retrieve metadata for an existing short URL
GET {{WeatherApi_HostAddress}}/api/urls/{{shortCode}}
Accept: application/json

### Follow the shortened link
GET {{WeatherApi_HostAddress}}/{{shortCode}}
